Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:30.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:37.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:44.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:51.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:01:00.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:05.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:10.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:16.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:22.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被鹦鹉螺号上的人们 当成小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强为此感到不服气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,立志要独力制作出直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.01,0:01:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却反而让他窥见大人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,认清自己还是个小孩的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诚实面对自己能力的不足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强请求韩森协助
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将直升机完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与娜蒂亚一同飞上蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而强为了实现自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,许愿自己能早日长大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:03.66,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#18 鹦鹉螺对鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰影看来是英国籍货船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该没有注意到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,维持现状直至对方 完全从视野中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来应该没什么问题\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们好久没这么接近陆地了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:03:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望上陆的那些家伙 能带回什么有用的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近倒是都没听到 海中怪物的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像已经被美国舰队 给解决掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听说那还是只 超过200公尺的怪物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能解决那么大只怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美国也挺了不起的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下子我们也能放心 在海上航行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让世人畏惧的怪物 现在也已经葬身海底了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们是在说鹦鹉螺号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听起来不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好\N你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么线索吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到处都查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰提斯的家伙们 隐藏得很彻底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除了这份报导 就没有其它消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『海中怪物终于葬身海底』吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近没有拦截到对方讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问过好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却没有收集到半点 长嘴硬鳞鱼号的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们终于停止破坏通商 开始执行真正的计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又要建造巴别塔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 那项计划已经彻底失败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是其它方面的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底会是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的工作就是要查出其内容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是空着手回去 不晓得该怎么跟尼莫船长交代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更令人害怕的 应该是艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不晓得如果就这样回去 会被她怎么念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,定时报告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本舰目前位置为W-25 N-306
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深度96公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成对消灭引擎一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辅助引擎一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,存粮还能支撑20天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于之前三次的战斗维修 造成资材不足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为应该 先返回基地一趟比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,视操舵长带回来的情报 再做决定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来当轮机士见习生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,害我的宝贝西装沾满了机油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们好像到过许多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欧洲可能已经在 世界的另一头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里究竟是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直都没看海图及罗盘 我也完全没概念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根据我昨天看到的星星位置 应该在很南方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来要到哪里去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰听令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本舰为了补给资材将前往基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？\N什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,御寒用品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,御寒用品？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用来保护身体不被冻伤的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不要穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么非得穿上 这种丑陋的衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的好丑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可没有勇气穿着这种衣服 站在尼莫船长面前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么要穿上这么丑的衣服呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我们要去南极
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要去南极？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是他说是要去基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要去基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种到处都是冰的地方 怎么盖得了基地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,况且在这世上根本没人晓得 南极从哪里开始是陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极是个那么难到的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至今从未有过任何船只 接近过南极
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强劲的风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及厚实的冰层
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加上轻易能让眼泪结冻的酷寒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全拒绝了人类的接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是那样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至今有许多人都向南极挑战过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却全部都失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:08:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算鹦鹉螺号是艘 再优秀的潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也无法战胜南极严苛的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 真是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要去南极 南极啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那究竟是个怎样的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好兴奋喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 你有去过吧 那是个怎样的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛 就是基地所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是个怎样的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛 就是基地所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛 就是基地所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是基地所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基地所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 那是个怎样的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是鹦鹉螺号的 秘密基地所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为大家的回答都是这句
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家应该是想让你们惊喜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 我就特别告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像魔法一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的 这是科学的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 它的原理是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是幻灯机吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是将电子脑 处理过的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藉由电力、磁力 以及电子的力量呈现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『电子脑』是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛 就是能够进行思考的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次我再详细向你说明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在是在谈这个对吧\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是南极大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 居然画出了海岸线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那有什么厉害？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人迹未至的南极大陆 海岸线一直为冰层所覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从没有人见过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船已经有那样的地图了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是怎么查出来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这并不是我们画的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是这艘船上的 电子脑画出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它是怎么晓得的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个记号是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是秘密基地的所在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是在大陆中心耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船根本到不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中途要用走的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题 就坐这艘船去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是要怎么去？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,半径20公里内未发现舰影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无电波障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空气压缩机启动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即将进入南极圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像要进入南极了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是流冰 体积还不大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,航道上出现障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是冰原 冰层厚度约5公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么处理？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,压缩空气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成至第48储气器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离完成还有两分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成后立刻准备潜航\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明到了南极 却不准我们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总比感冒生病好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还是想看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰潜航准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全员就潜航位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要到舰桥去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,潜航装置 一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深度60 压载正常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰首11至两点钟方向 出现巨大冰山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,左舷30度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深度80 舵维持不变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了 这一带水温超过7度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 海底…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真惨 简直就是海底坟场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长 分析海水成分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:13:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地磁场呈现不稳定状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海水浓度上升0.75
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,二氧化碳、硫化氢及重金属离子 高于平常200倍之多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是海底火山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还以为这一带都是死火山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大自然总是令人惊奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法 绕道而行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是海底火山喷发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火山？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海中也有火山吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极真是个麻烦的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进入冰层下方 深度160
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发现不明航行物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正从11点钟方向接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相对速度约60海浬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难不成是长嘴硬鳞鱼号？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,10秒钟以内确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未发现机械声及引擎声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无磁力反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并非长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那会是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点头绪也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰就战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰就战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重复一次 全舰就战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回则是要开战吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极真的比传说中 还要来得危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过来了 确实是朝着我方而来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有600
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,降下潜舵 垂直下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生物？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而…而且还跟乌贼很像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上方是冰层 下方居然是乌贼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱…抱歉 擦撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是生物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们闯进它的势力范围了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又要过来了 左舷前方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两舷全速 右满舷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 会直接撞上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全员做好冲击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,几亿年前的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕 会被它压扁的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是单凭这艘船的武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无法攻击附着于舰桥的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:17:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,硬化玻陨石被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关闭装甲门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长 在船身释放高压电流如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好主意\N好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,试试看吧 副船长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺… 也就是鹦鹉螺对鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点都不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最大电压\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:18:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,行不通吗？\N行不通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎全开 垂直上升
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是上方是冰山…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧 带着鹦鹉螺撞上去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点都没效 真恐怖的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比长嘴硬鳞鱼号还难对付
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样下去舰桥撑不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,右舷到底 航道107
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是那边有海底火山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧 就是107
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧 直接冲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么做…鹦鹉螺号会熔解的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但也没有其它方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,排出至30号为止的压缩空气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,排气完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要冲进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前依然健在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:21:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,操舵长 尽可能的靠近喷火口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看谁撑得久是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰外温度1200度 舰内40度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回则是热死人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极是所有难关的集合吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这种高温下竟然还能存活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.73,0:21:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是恐怖的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,舰桥快撑不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对方是生物 一定会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙是生物 在里头无法呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 没想到那样的生物 还存活至今
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自然界还有许多 人们无法理解的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,航道20 朝基地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒 海底竟然会有那样的隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是无人知晓的海底隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.09,0:22:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,离开水中通道 进入海中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.48,0:23:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 这里明明是大陆中央 竟然还有这么一片大海
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 这里就是 地图所标示的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 巨大的地下洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:54.75,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:24:02.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:07.99,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.06,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:21.24,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:31.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.48,0:24:40.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.29,0:24:44.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.50,0:24:49.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.27,0:24:58.37,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.19,0:25:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南极秘密基地上方 有一座巨大的冰之宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.02,0:25:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 这是我的朋友 伊里恩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.70,0:25:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是你的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.40,0:25:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 也是这种生物的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.67,0:25:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长的好友伊里恩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.60,0:25:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮我解开了 我想知道的谜团之一
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.47,0:25:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.94,0:25:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『尼莫的好友』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.41,0:25:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔
